title: 4 Diverse Books - February 2014 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 4 diverse books (3 PDFs + 1 MOBI) for February 2014:

1. Elasticity - Theory, Applications, and Numerics (3rd Ed) by Martin H. Sadd (Feb 21, 2014)
   
2. Global Safety of Fresh Produce - A Handbook of Best Practice, Innovative Commercial Solutions and Case Studies by Jeffrey Hoorfar (Feb 14, 2014)
   
3. Hygiene in Food Processing - Principles and Practice (2nd Ed) by Huub Lelieveld, John Holah and David Napper (Jan 2, 2014)
   
4. The Survival Medicine Handbook - A Guide for When Help is Not on the Way by Joseph Alton and Amy Alton (Jun 13, 2013)
